{"tid":158741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國校園槍響4傷　17歲嫌擁步槍、手榴彈","createTime":"2017-03-16T13:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T14:42:48.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8dd14071236836e0ba914c5a4cd014d3606354","tid":158741,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">法國校園槍響4傷　17歲嫌擁步槍、手榴彈<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170316/1078085/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170316%2F1078085%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6e7a70a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170316/1078085/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170316/640_77faeef8a644325d091bdd016027d51d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170316%2F640_77faeef8a644325d091bdd016027d51d.jpg&h=7f2737c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20 minutes報導，法國南部濱海阿爾卑斯省格拉斯鎮（Grasse）一間中學傳出槍響，至少4人受傷。特警已經逮捕1人並封鎖校園，還有1人在逃。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，被捕17歲學生被捕時有一把步槍，2把手槍，2顆手榴彈，過去沒有案底。<br />\n<br />\n地方政府指出，事件是兩學生間嫌隙，與恐怖攻擊無關。（余浚安／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"873f9cfeb49b62bd0cb9d2f2f904ca221c73b2f5","tid":158741,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40f9e736ca7c43bb9fb478666981f1cb3d8c515","tid":158741,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}